{"tid":1414921,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"封路太嚴重，有淺黃家庭反感","createTime":"2019-08-05T12:58:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T14:39:14.000Z","uid":263448,"like":25,"dislike":67,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"666256c1c3598ee4a417c2cd2d2a8639b171ceda","tid":1414921,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:58:57.000Z","msg":"轉淺黃家庭<br />\n<br />\n有公司因為示威活動，提早收鋪，提早放工。<br />\n4點收工，但坐巴士，番黎要行馬路番，有人中途跌倒。<br />\n行到8點先到家。<br />\n<br />\n至少2宗同樣情況。<br />\n佢地不滿番工受阻，放工又受阻。<br />\n受到傷害結果又間接傷害無辜既人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好唔重視淺黃支持者。<br />\n我係過來人，我明白家人間接受傷，會怨恨示威者果種心情。"},{"pid":"1704afe469d14ab4c399bcd8e70a683cedf15cb9","tid":1414921,"uid":84102,"like":7,"dislike":8,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:00:19.000Z","msg":"吓 sor9 我屋企人深藍都撐反政府wor  多謝林鄭"},{"pid":"527d0680eda8125b791060edd4004f0726a0a417","tid":1414921,"uid":21819,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:00:52.000Z","msg":"過左兩個月<br />\n如果遲幾個鍾返屋企 會動搖到你對呢件事既睇法叫淺藍喎"},{"pid":"25ae99a3e6e819a8b3077fa4ccc6909d28142561","tid":1414921,"uid":50088,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:01:02.000Z","msg":"屌你呢d p牌低質帶風向就收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cab52b54cc180e063927dad448ce5f441dbef80","tid":1414921,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"25ae99a3e6e819a8b3077fa4ccc6909d28142561","tid":1414921,"uid":50088,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:01:02.000Z","msg":"屌你呢d p牌低質帶風向就收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:02:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AkxqUB0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAkxqUB0.jpg&h=574c886b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"222e14a55250eee7595073353938f45246a6d70b","tid":1414921,"uid":68084,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:02:48.000Z","m